<section xmlns:ns0="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <num>1-617.14</num>
  <heading>Timeliness of decisions.</heading>
  <text>All decisions of the Board shall be rendered within a reasonable period of time, and in no event later than 120 days after the matter is submitted or referred to it for a decision.</text>
